items.name: Scissors
items.description: Used for cutting hair & other materials!

items.name: Fiber
items.description: Delicately collected strands of plant.  Perfect for making thread, cloth, or rope.

items.name: Flint
items.description: Ferroceric flint that holds an edge better than regular stone.

items.name: Stone
items.description: A hefty chunk of stone.

items.name: Wood
items.description: A thick, sturdy cutting from a tree.

items.name: Metal Arrow
items.description: An armor-and-hide piercing metal arrow.

items.name: Compound Bow
items.description: A high-tech bow made of durable alloy, can launch arrows at high velocity.  Requires arrows to fire.

items.name: Flame Arrow
items.description: Lights the target on fire, and can also light oil slicks.

items.name: Bow
items.description: Masters of the bow often became great conquerers.  Requires arrows to fire.

items.name: Bolt
items.description: A basic bolt with a flint arrowhead.  If it doesn't break, you can recover your ammo.

items.name: Stone Arrow
items.description: A basic arrow with a flint arrowhead.  If it doesn't break, you can recover your ammo.

items.name: Bow
items.description: Masters of the bow often became great conquerers.  Requires arrows to fire.

items.name: Blood Pack
items.description: Use this to replace lost blood.  Restores Health over time.

items.name: Grenade
items.description: Pulling the pin starts a 5 second timer to an explosion.  Make sure you've thrown it by then.

items.name: Oil Jar
items.description: Throw it to create an oil slick which can be lit on fire! This sticky substance can also slow down people which step in it!

items.name: Plant Species Z Fruit
items.description: Bioluminescent Fruit that provides a flash of Charge lighting

items.name: Poison Grenade
items.description: Releases narcotic smoke to knock out anything in the area -- only affects humans.

items.name: Smoke Grenade
items.description: Releases a lot of smoke to obscure your plans. Pulling the pin starts a 5 second timer to an explosion.

items.name: AnglerGel
items.description: A thick, viscous substance that can sustain a flame for a remarkably long duration.

items.name: Electric Prod
items.description: Powerful stunning weapon, but can only be used for a single strike before recharge is needed.

items.name: Pike
items.description: A powerful melee weapon tipped with metal.  Unlike the Spear, it cannot be thrown.

items.name: Spear
items.description: A easily made melee weapon that can also be thrown.  Has a chance to break when used.

items.name: Sword
items.description: The undisputed ruler of short-range combat. Needs a hotter flame to be forged.

items.name: Flamethrower Ammo
items.description: Fuel for the flamethrower.

items.name: Flamethrower
items.description: The fastest way to roast a target.

items.name: Rocket Propelled Grenade
items.description: A small but powerful explosive, primarily used with rocket launchers.

items.name: Rocket Launcher
items.description: Mankind's ultimate portable killing device.

items.name: Simple Shotgun Ammo
items.description: A few simple bullets in a hide casing, used with forged shotguns.

items.name: Shotgun
items.description: Very powerful up close, but less reliable with range.

items.name: Crossbow
items.description: Has signifantly more power than the Bow, but cannot fire rapidly.  Can fire underwater.

items.name: Slingshot
items.description: A simple ranged weapon that deals damage from afar.  Better for knocking out a target than killing it outright.  Requires stone to fire.

items.name: Bear Trap
items.description: Immobilizes humans and small creatures.

items.name: C4 Charge
items.description: This advanced explosive can annihilate structures.

items.name: C4 Remote Detonator
items.description: This device uses radio waves to detonate all primed C4 packages on the same frequency.

items.name: Improvised Explosive Device
items.description: Place two of these near each other to create an explosive trap.

items.name: Grappling Hook
items.description: Apply on the Crossbow to grapple onto the environment & other creatures. Primary Fire to "Reel-In", Secondary Fire to "Reel-Out", Crouch to Detach, Jump + Reel-In to Vault-Jump!

items.name: Crossbow
items.description: Has signifantly more power than the Bow, but cannot fire rapidly.  Can fire underwater.

items.name: Spear Bolt
items.description: A massive bolt with a cast iron arrowhead. Can only be used in a Ballista Turret or Harpoon Gun. If it doesn't break, you can recover your ammo.

items.name: Harpoon Launcher
items.description: Has tremendous power and speed underwater, but ineffective range out of water. Uses Spear Bolts for ammunition.

items.name: Net Projectile
items.description: High-speed projectile that unfurls to ensnare creatures in netting. Can only be fired from a Harpoon Launcher.

items.name: Net Gun
items.description: Has tremendous power and speed underwater, but ineffective range out of water. Uses Spear Bolts for ammunition.

items.name: Parachute
items.description: Use this while falling to slow your fall. Use again while parachuting to deactivate it.

items.name: Spyglass
items.description: This instrument, while primitive, is quite effective at long-range reconnaissance.
